  [@@unboxed] [@@noalloc]
(** [round x] rounds [x] to the nearest integer with ties (fractional
    values of 0.5s) rounded away from zero, regardless of the current
    rounding direction.  If [x] is an integer, [+0.s], [-0.s], [nan], or
