  [@@unboxed] [@@noalloc]
(** [copy_sign x y] returns a float whose absolute value is that of [x]
    and whose sign is that of [y].  If [x] is [nan], returns [nan].
    If [y] is [nan], returns either [x] or [-. x], but it is not
    specified which. *)

